lls;\n        }\n\n        private void setName(String name) {\n            this.name = name;\n            setterCalls++;\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777347178855}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_HqqBtEBbjTm7NvtBXyRiyJ9j|fc_08c74b9fb34b62d60169f02a6aabb081959f03145480679604", "toolName": "bash", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "(no output)\n\nCommand exited with code 1"}], "details": {}, "isError": true, "timestamp": 1777347178855}]}
