etadata will be necessary, focusing on direct reflection.\n\n**Understanding constructor invocation**\n\nI need to consider invoking a constructor using `Constructor.newInstance` in a native image. It seems like I’ll need an unconditional method entry for `<init>`. Using `getDeclaredConstructor` could mean I need to consider `queryAllDeclaredConstructors` or specific method entries. I'm not entirely sure if those specific entries allow lookup too. Generally, Graal reflection config method entries support both lookup and invocation, but I want to be certain of that before proceeding.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_08c74b9fb34b62d60169f02b22d55c8195ae8e8204cc156595\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp8CtFY4nHTJCLyZNPgwfDgiE7m14QwL-gpNYzv8w14OFkPnA_kuFu6aiA7fC9IHTEkaERrYYI4RxTptJCwHAUQrPyUWmK-yWYgTgZ5q-kEztZnSjiFnrH6ib5hDP9qK9Mb2jqciIdNhJmZauHngoD2Fj3U92C1xVspJ3H3cMvB7cCRAIbiP0q3bEXUymtMGVIViyf3q50h4jNsGzWoSQ-dgPG_Lc8Vf0e_u0-EmT2g-AP84uM5Qofye4o_qhbJuOpjpMBsr74eydiWapvd_ER1V5ioGIS6QDfYTCfis6uqT4nLSFIyImMJoKB_S8Oj0B-yFxd5pLnTDK-vRkTaA-nS-bu8774sdibgrKaNJ4XwlxfvOm9V4VXlJH35hfRZ7DL4H2DXXEfNP3LxbJggjSPM3xnjTPMSk5NXLGExL__SXaNj3kZTWil93RlEY5bValkNxUjkIGJvs-NGG6EXVtL0YHK6cxsf2vaEu7KZ0Enf0UrNOG0ZGY5YD6XwnSeOCaGi9YCQ3nnr8jytjs_EUmPUrPXULTGX94YgYFRpsVjMTl0gm0y5O-a5HUEksr7LiQEpiZFb8Gwwej1PkfMAeGuAblEk8eJEakcQIT6oPgRSU7rSI17AmxK51f8ry3COCshsYJet45KO0_mHmB3HRRHpLSH-le5GBr8Fdz6Md4uKax_O_HlqDtzNo3z_A_WUkgMoerAhK-LdE0J9qkJWrMMjgSVMhtjpW66HkTn2GFx12p6iPpf6F15uTCtffT7WcMucZfcxmgzTvhIOrA571WMmmf2xFWFMTvAaw5Fso-NQy0XopYehVrx4x7A7-qiQ7VHzlUI5RY_I9C7dqSWZxf5RhBWbdwq7DTxawDyRI9ZNaJa5Ci_hqvi_rNmlYZGgW8yKeNnoInTu7lQt6u_OaRBqaoRP5vWVLr79H6_JxKQNr4Hbk3Nh8XpJgHwhTi9Y9tDEizagpp87cvSgLzxBYMhlkcuZyHl5EAyn2qbjR--Hs4yRf-PLRc24OJRcEd_NpThKqHy7mrX7j-kteSlQDKT-G4_5Mr_vc35cfmAPDgZY-e7Lkb9LqHT02ShYyFzSpGdWDo7xZ0WErVzlQal7oGu294jsltgBdlbOgGMbrRVGNhq8qgo_HLcIi-WQ3G-PAEuBsx_OEnAASjYxAmVvdicoinn7twtemw6XWIZf10w_GGJjW8ykCp9U2p3_8yGSrZ3rWJoOsBPaKFj1GCS1lITk_KTkZJ6RAGcLLsxlAKI_YUnhjaLY